under old Citicorp mortgage programmes that were discontinued in 1991.
Since then, the bank claims, the performance of its mortgage portfolio has
improved. Earlier this year, Citicorp announced a Dollars 1bn non-recourse
commitment with the Federal National Mortgage Association (Fannie Mae),
