shares and warrants at a price equivalent to asset value on January 15.
Holders will be entitled to new units on a two-for-five basis.
The trust said that the additional funds 'will enable the company to invest
in a cost-effective manner in a greater number of US smaller companies
without reducing the size of its individual holdings.'
